### PROJECT OVERVIEW
**Name:** InboxAutopsy
**Tagline:** Diagnose why your email inbox is overwhelming you.
**Concept:** It is a digital wellbeing tool. It connects to the user's Gmail, fetches only the METADATA of their last 500 emails (Sender, Subject, Date, Read/Unread status), and passes that JSON to an LLM. The LLM acts as an "Email Therapist" and generates an "Inbox Health Report" with exactly ONE actionable fix. It does NOT read email bodies. It does NOT auto-reply.

